title: Frank Caliendo, NFL Week 13 Preview And Picks, Brian Kelly Is A Southerner & We All Read Frank Caliendo, NFL Week 13 Preview And Picks, Brian Kelly Is A Southerner & We All Read An Article On The MLB Lockout
description:
Taysom Hill might not be the guy and the Cowboys beat the Saints on TNF. Brian Kelly is now a Southerner.(00:02:16-00:16:57).
